message: "If you use AgentOS in research or a product, please cite it as below."
title: "AgentOS: a repo-local operating system for AI coding agents"
abstract: >-
  AgentOS is a repo-local operating layer for AI coding agents. It combines explicit
  task finish conditions, evidence-aware completion, selective project memory, and
  runtime adapters for Claude Code and OpenAI Codex. The main model performs semantic
  judgment while hooks restore attention and enforce deterministic runtime boundaries.
